thread.title: anne

author: anne
title: anne
text:
Loved the software which is mainly very user friendly and versatile, and the resulting book. This however had a page inserted in the wrong place. On complaining, a new book was immediately printed and sent out
There was a hic-cup in the software for my second book, but this was rectified by Customer Services very promptly.
Because of these two incidents I can't quite afford five stars.
I am however delighted with the quality of the books and on the strength of this alone, they would deserve five stars
I would highly recommend them.
